name: Relatedconditions_COPDI10
title: relatedconditions_COPD I10
description: J15.6 becomes non-billable 2024; no change needed to definition
purpose: (Clinical Focus: Conditions (problems and diagnoses) that are related to COPD. Used to distinguish problem list entries related to COPD from those which are not related to COPD.),(Data Element Scope: CONDITION: RELATED: COPD),(Inclusion Criteria: Billable ICD-10-CM codes in the chapter J40-J47 Chronic lower respiratory diseases),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes J47 Bronchiectasis, as well as other cardiopulmonary diseases)
